 "remarks": "Here is YOUR opportunity to join this robust community. Conveniently located in the heart of downtown Stamford! Each room in this 2 bedroom unit is oversized and offers ample room to stretch out. Primary bedroom offers a wall of closets and is huge! The 2nd bedroom is a good size and has a large closet. Updated full bathroom with tub/shower combination. There are SO many closets in this unit you will run out of things to put in them! The open Living Room/Dining Room allows for flexible entertaining. Large deck directly off the living room offers an outdoor space to relax, get some fresh air and offers a view of the city! Convenient to downtown Stamford and public transportation. Pool, exercise room, laundry room and 24 gated security service and more. Make YOUR move!",
